<section class="mb-44 mt-32 md:mt-48 opinion-section ">
  
  <h2 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-14 font-special tracking-wider">
    What <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-theme-red to-[#7a00b3] bg-clip-text text-transparent">my clients</span> say
  </h2>

  <p class="text-2xl mb-5">
    Want to know what my clients think about my work? Here are some
    of the comments I've received.
  </p>

  <swiper-container
    class="mySwiper"
    space-between="30"
    slides-per-view="auto"
    pagination="true"
    pagination-clickable="true"
    autoplay="true"
    autoplay-delay="3000"
    loop="true"
  >
    <swiper-slide class="testimonial-slide flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
      <p>
        "Simply the best! Since I started getting my nails done with her, they
        last for weeks intact. She always recommends what's best for my nail type
        and her designs are a work of art. 100% recommended."
      </p>
      <span class="mt-4 font-light">— Camila R.</span>
    </swiper-slide>

    <swiper-slide class="testimonial-slide flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
      <p>
        "Not only did I leave with beautiful nails, but I also felt super well
        taken care of. The environment is relaxing, clean, and she is super professional.
        You can tell she loves what she does."
      </p>
      <span class="mt-4 font-light">— Valentina M.</span>
    </swiper-slide>

    <swiper-slide class="testimonial-slide flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
      <p>
        "I'm very demanding with my nails, and I can say I found my
        ideal manicurist. Punctual, detail-oriented, and with excellent quality
        products. I wouldn't change her for anything!"
      </p>
      <span class="mt-4 font-light">— Andrea L.</span>
    </swiper-slide>

    <swiper-slide class="testimonial-slide flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
      <p>
        "Every appointment is an experience. I relax, treat myself, and leave happy with
        my beautiful nails."
      </p>
      <span class="mt-4 font-light">— Lucía T.</span>
    </swiper-slide>

    <swiper-slide class="testimonial-slide flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
      <p>
        "Not only is she talented, but she's also super friendly. It feels like visiting
        a friend."
      </p>
      <span class="mt-4 font-light">— Belén T.</span>
    </swiper-slide>
  </swiper-container>
</section>

<script
  src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-element-bundle.min.js"
></script>

<style>
  swiper-container {
    width: 100%;
    height: 40vh;
  }

  swiper-slide {
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 80%;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    
    border-top-right-radius: 1rem;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 1rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(180%);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px) saturate(180%);
    background-color: rgba(229, 72, 75, 0.135);

    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px); /* Safari support */

    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;

    /* transition: transform 0.3s ease; */
  }
  swiper-slide::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0%;
    left: 0%;
    width: 500px;
    height: 300px;
    background: rgba(252, 0, 0, 0.5);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(100px);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: -1;
  }
  swiper-slide::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 80%; /* Ajusta según el lugar deseado */
    left: 80%;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: rgba(141, 0, 212, 0.488);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0.3; /* Opcional: menos visible que el primero */
  }

  swiper-slide:nth-child(2n) {
    width: 70%;
  }

  swiper-slide:nth-child(3n) {
    width: 70%;
  }

</style>
